transcript:
Customer: Hello.

Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello sir, Akshay sir se baat karni thi, woh abhi call receive nahi kar rahe.
Executive: Ji ji mam Akshay baat kar raha hu, aap hi ka call gaya raha tha, aap hi ka call aa gayi.
Customer: Ha ji, main isliye.
Customer: Accha Akshay.
Executive: Ji mam.
Customer: Aap call receive nahi kyu kar rahe the sir?
Executive: Mam main main dusre room mein raha jo off hota hai na.
Executive: Saturday ko. Toh phone dekha nahi, phone bhi gaya tha. Bataye kya ho gaya, koi issue aa raha mam?
Customer: Ha issue aa raha tha isliye call kiye the.
Executive: Ha bataye.

Executive: Aapki aawaz kat kat ke aa rahi hai mam.

Customer: Ha ji, ab aa rahi hai kya?
Executive: Abhi bhi kat rahi hai mam.
Executive: Bataye, main sun raha hu aapke.
Customer: Sir abhi inquiries nahi aa rahi hai.
Executive: Ji.
Executive: Aap mere wohi wale number pe wapas call karoge mam, 8285 wale pe.
Customer: Ha theek hai.
Executive: Uspe main call receive kar lunga, please.
Customer: Theek hai, theek hai.
